Christopher P. Mottern



Mr. Christopher P. Mottern, CPA, is on the Board of Directors at Farmer Brothers Co. Mr. Mottern was previously employed as President, Chief Executive Officer & Director by Peet's Coffee & Tea, Inc. and President & Chief Executive Officer by Capri Sun, Inc. He also served on the board at Valley Media, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Connecticut.



